rofiling of regulated entities.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2><strong>2.3.TIRA RBS Repository<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>TIRA RBS Repository safely and securely stores all data related to regulated institutions. The Repository records all institutional profile information, data collected from regulated institutions and analytical data generated by the regulator. A complete system-wide audit trail is also maintained. Its is fully searchable giving you access to an unparalleled amount of regulatory and supervisory information, all in one place.<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"a4e9a3a9a6d71c0a2440aab1d42e62ca.jpeg\",\"featured\":0,\"active\":\"1\",\"slug\":\"rbss-informations\",\"call_to_action_en\":\"Go to Service Now\",\"call_to_action_sw\":\"Ingia Sasa\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/apps.tira.go.tz\\/TIRARBSPortal\\/\",\"created_at\":\"2022-03-07T11:01:23.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-08-12T10:09:11.000000Z\",\"user_id\":0,\"icon\":\"icon-1659878969\",\"color\":null,\"specials\":null}','2022-08-12 07:09:50','2022-08-12 07:09:50'),(1382,1,'Service','update','154.118.225.10','http://demo8.eganet.go.tz/tira/cms/services/5','{\"id\":5,\"title_sw\":\"TIRA RBS System Portal\",\"title_en\":\"TIRA RBS System Portal\",\"summary_sw\":null,\"summary_en\":null,\"content_sw\":\"<p>TIRA RBS System Portal<\\/p>\",\"content_en\":\"<p>TIRA RBS System Portal<\\/p>\",\"photo_url\":\"a4e9a3a9a6d71c0a2440aab1d42e62ca.jpeg\",\"featured\":0,\"active\":\"1\",\"slug\":\"tira-rbs-system-portal\",\"call_to_action_en\":\"Go to Service Now\",\"call_to_action_sw\":\"Ingia Sasa\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/apps.tira.go.tz\\/TIRARBSPortal\\/\",\"created_at\":\"2021-09-11T12:24:32.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-08-07T15:25:34.000000Z\",\"user_id\":0,\"icon\":\"icon-1659885934\",\"color\":null,\"specials\":null}','2022-08-12 07:10:34','2022-08-12 07:10:34'),(1383,1,'Service','update','154.118.225.10','http://demo8.eganet.go.tz/tira/cms/services/4','{\"id\":4,\"title_sw\":\"TIRA MIS Portal\",\"title_en\":\"